

                                     🛠️ Backend (The Engine)
Built on Node.js and Express, the backend manages data, security, and the core business logic.
Database Architecture: Integrated MongoDB for flexible data management (Products, Categories, Users, Orders).
Authentication & Security:
Web Layer: Session-based authentication with express-session and bcryptjs for secure password hashing.
API Layer: Stateless JWT (JSON Web Token) authentication for external integrations or future mobile apps.
Role-Based Access: Specialized middleware (ensureAdmin, ensureAuth) to protect administrative routes and paid content.
Product & Media Logic:
Secure Video Delivery: A custom media proxy that verifies a user's purchase status before serving video files.
Resource Categorization: Support for different product types: Courses, Books, IELTS, Level Tests, and Free Resources.
Automated Data Seeding: System automatically initializes default categories and an admin account on first run.
Order System:
Telegram Integration: A "Buy Now" flow that generates pre-filled Telegram messages for instant conversion.
Access Management: Orders for digital categories automatically grant access to all products within that category once "paid."
File Handling: Integrated multer for managing category thumbnails and product image/video uploads.

                                🎨 Frontend (The Experience)

The frontend is a "Premium Mobile-First" interface built with EJS templates and a high-end Vanilla CSS design system.
Design Aesthetic:
Glassmorphism: Modern UI using backdrop blurs, translucent cards, and subtle gradients for a high-end, "Apple-style" feel.
Dark Mode: Native support for dark themes with curated color palettes.
Mobile-First Grid System:
2-Column Card Grid: Optimized for mobile devices to maximize content density without clutter.
Horizontal Scroll Carousels: Swipeable sections for "Featured Products" and "Categories" to keep the vertical height manageable.
Key Components:
Hero Section: High-impact introduction with cinematic calls to action.
Smart Navbar: Integrated search bar and responsive menu with login/logout states.
Dynamic Product Cards: Intelligent cards that change buttons based on access status (Buy Now vs. Watch Now).
Responsive Filter Bar: Quick filtering by category, price (free/premium), and product type.
Interactive Features:
Cart System: Client-side cart persistence using localStorage for a smooth shopping experience.
Cinematic Backgrounds: High-performance animated backgrounds (like the monsoon storm effect) to "wow" users on landing.
Micro-animations: Subtle hover effects and scale transitions for touch interaction feedback.